{"tid":97042,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟鳴人同佐助嘅最強時期係幾時？","createTime":"2017-01-27T10:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T14:32:37.000Z","uid":27632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b40d851e70b6e61d491301644c58586c1b980079","tid":97042,"uid":27632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:58:40.000Z","msg":"打六道老母嗰陣，the last嗰陣，定係Road to boruto嗰陣？<br />\n根據終極風暴4嘅佐助，佢嘅奧義有建御雷神，千鳥&middot;星碎，地爆天星&middot;天墜"},{"pid":"61dc1d41d8ac076d18f7e662b90ca460199916a2","tid":97042,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:00:54.000Z","msg":"我覺得六道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672859026cdb84f83886a355f79ea940a293ccd8","tid":97042,"uid":1888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:15:05.000Z","msg":"應該係打老母果陣<br />\n嗚人打完之後尾獸都各散東西只得番九尾同各尾獸既小小查克拉<br />\n<br />\n佐助打完之後係得到輪迴眼，但佢跛左隻手打死都唔駁番應該有影響"},{"pid":"3cf40e1a4411c438e4ce3e27c1211d9b87809a8a","tid":97042,"uid":27632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得六道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n理論上打六道老母嗰陣佢哋有六道之力，應該係最強，因為佢哋封印完老母之後就冇咗六道之力<br />\n鳴人冇求道玉（應該廢咗），不過佐助嘅輪迴寫輪眼仲係度喎，姐係佐助冇廢到？"},{"pid":"0610b4e8ef0f2496b092f9133838a3ea742bac07","tid":97042,"uid":30235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:19:16.000Z","msg":"細個互嘴嗰一刻最勁"},{"pid":"67759dbff21d969e7f4b7e8862f6ebd6059b5604","tid":97042,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"口遁最強"},{"pid":"cd368200179354f4a78cc559b5fd55ec122f229f","tid":97042,"uid":1861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:24:20.000Z","msg":"鳴門就肯定係打輝夜嗰陣架喇，佐助就road to boruto嘅時候最勁，始終已經可以純熟咁運用輪迴眼"},{"pid":"a890f1e4838e615dce4aead03378423ea9be04bc","tid":97042,"uid":78198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:32:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳴門就肯定係打輝夜嗰陣架喇，佐助就road to boruto嘅時候最勁，始終已經可以純熟咁運用輪迴眼</blockquote><br />\n但佐助打完老母之後就唔識用六道堆技呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6adc431910abb698127e496dd67bbfb4036e1e20","tid":97042,"uid":1861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鳴門就肯定係打輝夜嗰陣架喇，佐助就road to boruto嘅時候最勁，始終已經可以純熟咁運用輪迴眼</blockquote><br />\n但佐助打完老母之後就唔識用六道堆技呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點樣唔識用六道堆技，輪迴眼都唔係因為得到陰之力先出現，係瀕死加兜俾嘅柱間細胞結合而出現，打完輝夜消失嘅只有陰之力，輪迴眼本身嘅技能全部仲喺到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df5cfe9447a0ad246aa572e2694232d493c0734","tid":97042,"uid":58076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:38:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鳴門就肯定係打輝夜嗰陣架喇，佐助就road to boruto嘅時候最勁，始終已經可以純熟咁運用輪迴眼</blockquote><br />\n但佐助打完老母之後就唔識用六道堆技呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為冇左六道力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢仲有眼，好唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836d7ff05bf7fbcfe5d5894bbe4d63ef608061fd","tid":97042,"uid":1861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳴門就肯定係打輝夜嗰陣架喇，佐助就road to boruto嘅時候最勁，始終已經可以純熟咁運用輪迴眼</blockquote><br />\n數漏左，如果計埋吸左九隻尾獸嘅話佐助就應該係用因陀羅之箭嗰刻最勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f22d93d09de1a6d84dbd1262b6e9b9696d9885","tid":97042,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:45:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鳴門就肯定係打輝夜嗰陣架喇，佐助就road to boruto嘅時候最勁，始終已經可以純熟咁運用輪迴眼</blockquote><br />\n數漏左，如果計埋吸左九隻尾獸嘅話佐助就應該係用因陀羅之箭嗰刻最勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又咪比鳴人大地之力尾獸玉解左"},{"pid":"1372111cb8a4c6da1fdac8ed7f2c579bbeac98ae","tid":97042,"uid":10884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T12:14:03.000Z","msg":"咁其實陰之力有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91c757cbd854b96486fc9b278252dc60862eca1","tid":97042,"uid":27632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:30:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁其實陰之力有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n理論上有，實際上冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02436f2b52264c9f1e0490c9a454327881811e01","tid":97042,"uid":31002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:32:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁其實陰之力有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n理論上有，實際上冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淨係用黎封輝夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c7f1cfb0b100c35233b2875112a3849c92682b","tid":97042,"uid":41326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"愈睇愈似龍珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643a7199ce44119cfc05267f1ee87514ac4202df","tid":97042,"uid":27632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:33:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳴門就肯定係打輝夜嗰陣架喇，佐助就road to boruto嘅時候最勁，始終已經可以純熟咁運用輪迴眼</blockquote><br />\n打老母之後，鳴門同佐助一對一打和，之後你話road to boruto嘅鳴門廢過之前，佐助勁咗，咁姐係Road to boruto嘅佐助勁過鳴門？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96df9667fd1685ad5182084383fd4c82c56e8b3","tid":97042,"uid":29621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:37:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鳴門就肯定係打輝夜嗰陣架喇，佐助就road to boruto嘅時候最勁，始終已經可以純熟咁運用輪迴眼</blockquote><br />\n打老母之後，鳴門同佐助一對一打和，之後你話road to boruto嘅鳴門廢過之前，佐助勁咗，咁姐係Road to boruto嘅佐助勁過鳴門？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實make sense<br />\n打完交之後鳴門做火影 無乜機會打交<br />\n但佐助仲係出面旅行緊<br />\n鳴門生疏曬 輸比佐助唔出奇"},{"pid":"edd8f7cb554160de02cac8d242f523cf831818f7","tid":97042,"uid":3179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:41:44.000Z","msg":"一定係陰陽之力後果陣既嗚佐<br />\n仙術九喇嘛融合  因陀羅須佐型態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bec08cf838c377fa0724974f6172f8e92a9c642","tid":97042,"uid":27632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:42:12.000Z","msg":"另外有冇人可以話我知，點解終極風暴4 嘅佐助冇得用因陀羅之箭，但係鳴門有得用六道&middot;超大玉螺旋手裏劍？"},{"pid":"e3124e6b446f138538f02a31ad35d1ed811638b8","tid":97042,"uid":1861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:43:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鳴門就肯定係打輝夜嗰陣架喇，佐助就road to boruto嘅時候最勁，始終已經可以純熟咁運用輪迴眼</blockquote><br />\n打老母之後，鳴門同佐助一對一打和，之後你話road to boruto嘅鳴門廢過之前，佐助勁咗，咁姐係Road to boruto嘅佐助勁過鳴門？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲野都係主觀嘅啫，始終冇交代兩個嘅實力進步到邊，不過以外傳入面黎講佐助嘅實力明顯比鳴門更勝一籌，換個角度黎講你都可以話係鳴門太耐冇打所以生疏左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0dc89f6e483a71cd7e002685afc33f2229b369","tid":97042,"uid":27632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:43:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定係陰陽之力後果陣既嗚佐<br />\n仙術九喇嘛融合  因陀羅須佐型態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佐助有六道陰之力嗰陣嘅須佐有唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我冇認真睇佢個樣<img